snippet.title: Temple Run+ (Official Launch Trailer) | Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Introducing Temple Run+

The endless running game that took the world by storm is BACK and available on Apple Arcade. Complete new Weekly Challenges and unlock exciting rewards never seen before in this classic game. Take a study break to play Temple Run+ on your Macbook…or grab the remote to play on the AppleTV in your living room. 

Get it now for your iOS, MacOS, and tvOS devices: apple.co/-TempleRun







Temple Run Social Pages:
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/TempleRun/​
Twitter - https://twitter.com/TempleRun​
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/templerun/
